= Gajim on postmarketOS =
== Installation ==
First setup the dependencies

    sudo apk add g++ python3-dev py3-gobject3 alpine-sdk openssl-dev libffi-dev gettext

Then download the source tarball from https://gajim.org/downloads.php?lang=en#source
unpack it, enter the directory and execute

    pip3 install --user .

